Breviturma Stöhr Stöhr, Boissin & Hoareau, 2013
;
Ophiarthrum Peters, 1851
;
Ophiocomella A.H. Clark, 1939
;
Ophiomastix Müller & Troschel, 1842
.

DORSAL DISC. Disc pentagonal to circular; flat (about same level as arms). Integument obscuring plates. Dorsal disc with granules; with concealed primary plates; with scales; with smooth spines (
O’Hara et al. 2018
) or without spines. Dorsal disc scale/plate without tubercles. Radial shield present; with granules; length less than one third of the disc radius; scalene (oblique) triangular.
